				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have heard over and over...our pets suck, they dont let us solo in tier 4 planes, they die in one melee round...blah blah. 
<br />

<br />
So, what would our pets be like at the level 66-70 range to make people think they were appropriately powered? I want hard numbers like max HP, max damage...not just "they need to survive more than one melee round". 
<br />

<br />
To make it easier...lets just talk about non focused or DPoC focused since that would be the majority (imo). 
<br />

<br />
Edit: I moved this myself...oops.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
