				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I wouldn't mind seeing a new type of quest system designed for the mage class. IMOHO if it would be possible to do a quest that would give the mage an item for his pet that would be permanently equiped his/her pet with that item.
<br />
Examples: 
<br />

<br />
MAGIC ITEM Pet-NO DROP
<br />
Slot: CHEST
<br />
AC: 60
<br />
STR: +20 DEX: +20 STA: +20  AGI: +20 HP: +200
<br />
SV FIRE: +25 SV DISEASE: +25 SV COLD: +25 SV POISON: +25
<br />
Spell Shield: +3 
<br />
Required level of 65.
<br />
Effect: Protection of Ro (worn)
